<h2 id="symbols">Symbols</h2>

<p>The last component of the card we changed was the element symbols. The original symbols were more artistry rendered but did not scale well when smaller than 32px. Therefore a team member came up with a simpler flatter, more scalable symbol.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/bc_iconsize.png" alt="" /></p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/bcsymbols.png" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="development">Development</h2>

<p>After the contract with our client ended, they took the design assets we created and implemented them into their game. While the client liked what we created, they modified our designs into their game. <strong>The following screens were not created by the design team, and is currently being developed by Group 6.</strong></p>

